Morris RUDNICK et al. v. Frederick S. DEITRICK, Receiver. No. 3277. Circuit Court of Appeals, First Circuit. Oct. 22, 1937. Emmanuel Kurland, of Boston, Mass. (David Stoneman, of Boston, Mass., on the brief), for appellants. Leo Wyman, of Boston, Mass. (A. J. Aldridge, of Boston, Mass., on the brief), for appellee.

Before BINGHAM, WILSON, and MORTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed, with costs to the appellee.
